# Question 17
DCStations %>%
  group_by(name, nbEmptyDocks) %>%
  summarise(total = sum(nbEmptyDocks)) %>%
  arrange(desc(total)) %>%
  tail(20)

  arrange(desc(total)) %>%
  tail(30)
